    <Content contentid="4469" contenttypeid="LCTN" desc="Location / Locale">
      <Description><![CDATA[<p>Villa 1880 is tucked away down a quiet lane in sought-after Batu Belig on the peaceful northern edge of Seminyak. An easy 10-minute stroll away is Batu Belig Beach; walking south along the black volcanic sand brings you to uber-trendy beach bars Tropicola, W Hotel and Potato Head, while northwards is La Laguna and Finns Beach Club.</p><p>The area’s many cafés and bars are moments away, among them Watercress and Hog Wild (previously Naughty Nuri’s), along with boutiques and lifestyle stores as eclectic as the villa itself. Central Seminyak and the surfing mecca of Canggu are both a mere 10-minute drive away.</p>]]></Description>
